Name: athena-gedit
Summary: A small but powerful text editor for GNOME, for Athena
License: GPL
Group: Applications/Editors
Provides: gedit = 2.2.0.1

Requires: athena-GConf2 athena-libgnomeui athena-libglade2
Requires: athena-libgnomeprintui athena-eel athena-glib2 athena-ORBit2
Requires: athena-libbonobo athena-bonobo-activation

%description
gEdit is a small but powerful text editor designed specifically for
the GNOME GUI desktop.  gEdit includes a plug-in API (which supports
extensibility while keeping the core binary small), support for
editing multiple documents using notebook tabs, and standard text
editor functions.
